#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&skanlite; is an image scanning application that does nothing more than scan "
"and save images."
msgstr ""
"&skanlite; je aplikacija za skeniranje slik, ki ne naredi nič drugega kot "
"skenira in shranjuje slik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&skanlite; is based on libksane, a &kde; interface for SANE library to "
"control image scanners."
msgstr ""
"&skanlite; temelji na libksane, &kde; vmesnik za knjižnico SANE za nadzor "
"slikovnih skenerjev."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
