msgstr "skener"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "images"
msgstr "slike"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&skanlite; is a simple image scanning application that does nothing more "
"than scan and save images. &skanlite; can open a save dialog for every image "
"scanned or save the images immediately in a specified folder with auto-"
"generated names and format. The user can also choose to show the scanned "
"image before saving."
msgstr ""
"&skanlite; je preprosta aplikacija za skeniranje slik, ki ne naredi nič "
"drugega kot skenira in shranjuje slike. &skanlite; lahko odpre pogovorno "
"okno za shranjevanje za vsako skenirano sliko ali takoj shrani slike v "
"določeno mapo s samodejno ustvarjenimi imeni in obliko. Uporabnik se lahko "
"odloči tudi za prikaz optično prebrane slike pred shranjevanjem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&skanlite; can save images in all the formats supported by &Qt;. For example "
"the following formats:"
msgstr ""
"&skanlite; lahko shrani slike v vseh formatih, ki jih podpira &Qt;. Na "
"primer naslednje oblike:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "png (8 and 16 bits per color)"
msgstr "png (8 in 16 bitov na barvo)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "jpeg, jpg, jpeg 2000"
msgstr "jpeg, jpg, jpeg 2000"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>bmp</para>"
msgstr "<para>bmp</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can check the status of your scanner support from the SANE project "
"website through the <ulink url=\"http://www.sane-project.org/sane-supported-"
"devices.html\">Supported Devices page on the SANE website</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Stanje podpore za optični bralnik lahko preverite na spletnem mestu projekta "
"SANE prek <ulink url=\"http://www.sane-project.org/sane-supported-devices."
"html\">strani Podprte naprave na spletnem mestu SANE</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &skanlite;"
msgstr "Uporaba &skanlite;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scanner Selection"
msgstr "Izbira optičnega bralnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A default scanner can be specified on the command line of &skanlite; using "
"<userinput>skanlite -d [device name]</userinput> in a terminal. If the "
"selected scanner cannot be opened or if no default scanner is provided, a "
"scanner selection dialog is opened."
msgstr ""
"Privzeti skener lahko določite v ukazni vrstici &skanlite; z uporabo "
"<userinput>skanlite -d [ime naprave]</userinput> v terminalu. Če izbranega "
"optičnega bralnika ni mogoče odpreti ali če ni privzetega optičnega "
"bralnika, se odpre pogovorno okno za izbiro optičnega bralnika."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&skanlite; scanner selection dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&skanlite; pogovorno okno za izbiro optičnega bralnika</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&skanlite; scanner selection dialog</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&skanlite; pogovorno okno za izbiro optičnega bralnika</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The user can choose the scanner to be used and press <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> to open the scanner. Pressing <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> will "
"cause &skanlite; to exit."
msgstr ""
"Uporabnik lahko izbere skener, ki ga bo uporabil, in pritisne <guibutton>V "
"redu</guibutton>, da odpre skener. Če pritisnete <guibutton>Prekliči</"
"guibutton>, bo &skanlite; končal."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>No scanner found</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Skenerja ni bilo mogoče najti</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>No scanner found</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skenerja ni bilo mogoče najti</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case no devices were found, maybe because the scanner is not plugged in "
"or switched off, correct that. Then the <guibutton>Reload device list</"
"guibutton> can be used to reload the list of scanners."
msgstr ""
"Če ni bila najdena nobena naprava, morda zato, ker optični bralnik ni "
"priključen ali izklopljen, to popravite. Nato lahko uporabite "
"<guibutton>Znova naloži seznam naprav</guibutton> za ponovno nalaganje "
"seznama skenerjev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Not all drivers/backends support this feature. In that case quit &skanlite;, "
"connect your scanner and restart the application."
msgstr ""
"Vsi gonilniki/zadnji deli ne podpirajo te funkcije. V tem primeru zaprite "
"&skanlite;, povežite optični bralnik in znova zaženite aplikacijo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "&skanlite; Main Window"
msgstr "&skanlite; Glavno okno"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&skanlite; main window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&skanlite; glavno okno</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&skanlite; main window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&skanlite; glavno okno</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the main window, the user has two sets of scan options: <guilabel>Basic "
"Options</guilabel> and <guilabel>Scanner Specific Options</guilabel>. The "
"<guilabel>Basic Options</guilabel> tab contains the most common parameters "
"that the SANE scanner backends provide, while the <guilabel>Scanner Specific "
"Options</guilabel> tab contains all the options of the backend. The options "
"listed here depend on SANE support for your driver: libksane (which "
"&skanlite; uses) should be able to display most of the types of parameters "
"that SANE provides (analog gamma tables are not supported at this time)."
msgstr ""
"V glavnem oknu ima uporabnik dva niza možnosti skeniranja: <guilabel>Osnovne "
"možnosti</guilabel> in <guilabel>Posebne možnosti optičnega bralnika</"
"guilabel>. Zavihek <guilabel>Osnovne možnosti</guilabel> vsebuje "
"najpogostejše parametre, ki jih nudijo ozadja optičnega bralnika SANE, "
"medtem ko zavihek <guilabel>Posebne možnosti optičnega bralnika</guilabel> "
"vsebuje vse možnosti ozadja. Tu navedene možnosti so odvisne od podpore SANE "
"za vaš gonilnik: libksane (ki ga uporablja &skanlite;) bi moral biti "
"sposoben prikazati večino vrst parametrov, ki jih nudi SANE (analogne tabele "
"gama trenutno niso podprte)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Scanner Specific Options tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Zavihek, specifične za optični bralnik</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Scanner Specific Options tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zavihek, specifične za optični bralnik</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The scanner specific options contains more detailed options of the backends. "
"&skanlite; (libksane) does not have any special handling for these options."
msgstr ""
"Posebne možnosti optičnega bralnika vsebujejo podrobnejše možnosti ozadja. "
"&skanlite; (libksane) nima posebne obravnave za te možnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are satisfied with your settings, you can use the little arrow on the "
"top of the options splitter. When clicked it collapses or expands the "
"options. The collapser can overlap the preview area, but fades away when the "
"mouse cursor moves out of the collapser."
msgstr ""
"Če ste zadovoljni s svojimi nastavitvami, lahko uporabite majhno puščico na "
"vrhu razdelilnika možnosti. Ko kliknete, se možnosti strnejo ali razširijo. "
"Strnjevalnik lahko prekriva območje predogleda, vendar zbledi, ko se kazalec "
"miške premakne ven iz strnjevalnika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scanning"
msgstr "Skeniranje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To scan an image, the user can start with a preview scan and then select the "
"part of the scan area to do the final scan on. The preview scan is started "
"by pressing the preview button."
msgstr ""
"Za skeniranje slike lahko uporabnik začne s predogledom skeniranja in nato "
"izbere del območja skeniranja, na katerem bo opravil končno skeniranje. "
"Skeniranje predogleda se začne s pritiskom na gumb za predogled."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Preview Button</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Gumb za predogled</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Preview Button</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Gumb za predogled</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the preview is scanned the area for the final image can be selected."
msgstr "Ko je predogled skeniran, lahko izberete območje za končno sliko."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Selection and zoom</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izbira in povečava</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Selection and zoom</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izbira in povečava</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To better select the image the user can zoom in, out, to the current "
"selection or zoom to fit the whole preview to the window."
msgstr ""
"Za boljši izbor slike lahko uporabnik poveča ali pomanjša trenutni izbor ali "
"poveča, da celoten predogled prilagodi oknu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The \"zoom to fit\" button</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Gumb \"pomanjšaj, da se prilega\"</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The \"zoom to fit\" button</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Gumb \"pomanjšaj, da se prilega\"</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the image is selected the final image can be acquired by pressing the "
"final scan button."
msgstr ""
"Ko je slika izbrana, lahko končno sliko pridobite s pritiskom na gumb za "
"končno skeniranje."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The final scan button</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Gumb za končno skeniranje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The final scan button</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Gumb za končno skeniranje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "You will see the progress of the scan."
msgstr "Videli boste napredek skeniranja."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Scanning in progress</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Skeniranje v teku</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Scanning in progress</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skeniranje v teku</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Preview before saving</guilabel> is selected in the settings, "
"the scanned image is displayed in a preview window as you can see below on "
"the screenshot. If <guibutton>Save</guibutton> is pressed, the image is "
"saved and if <guibutton>Discard</guibutton> is pressed the preview is "
"discarded and you return to the main window."
msgstr ""
"Če je v nastavitvah izbran <guilabel>Predogled pred shranjevanjem</"
"guilabel>, se optično prebrana slika prikaže v oknu za predogled, kot lahko "
"vidite spodaj na posnetku zaslona. Če pritisnete <guibutton>Shrani</"
"guibutton>, se slika shrani in če pritisnete <guibutton>Zavrzi</guibutton>, "
"se predogled zavrže in vrnete se v glavno okno."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Preview Window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Okno za predogled</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Preview Window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Okno za predogled</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scanning Multiple Selections"
msgstr "Skeniranje več izbir"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes you need only certain parts of an image. Instead of scanning the "
"whole picture and then using a graphics application (&eg; &kolourpaint;) to "
"save the different image parts into separate files, use &skanlite;'s "
"multiple selection feature."
msgstr ""
"Včasih potrebujete le določene dele slike. Namesto skeniranja celotne slike "
"in nato uporabe grafične aplikacije (&eg; &kolourpaint;) za shranjevanje "
"različnih delov slike v ločene datoteke, uporabite &skanlite; funkcijo "
"večkratne izbire."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Multiple Selections</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Več izbir</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Multiple Selections</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Več izbir</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scan a preview and then use the &LMB; to select the first part of the image "
"in the preview. Hover the selected area with mouse cursor and click on the "
"green <guiicon>+</guiicon> icon to select the area. Selected areas are "
"indicated by a red border. Now select the next parts of the image in the "
"same way."
msgstr ""
"Skenirajte predogled in nato uporabite &LMB; da izberete prvi del slike v "
"predogledu. Z miškinim kazalcem premaknite izbrano območje in kliknite "
"zeleno ikono <guiicon>+</guiicon>, da izberete območje. Izbrana območja so "
"označena z rdečo obrobo. Zdaj na enak način izberite naslednje dele slike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a single selection hover the area with the mouse cursor and click "
"on the red <guiicon>-</guiicon> icon. With <guilabel>Clear Selections</"
"guilabel> from the context menu launched with the &RMB; all selections in a "
"preview can be removed."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti posamezen izbor, se pomaknite na območje z miško in "
"kliknite rdečo ikono <guiicon>-</guiicon>. Z <guilabel>Počisti izbire</"
"guilabel> iz priročnega menija, ki ga zaženete z &RMB; vse izbire v "
"predogledu je mogoče odstraniti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you placed two separate images or photos on you scanner and started a "
"preview &skanlite; automatically preselect the different areas. This "
"behaviour can be switched off in the settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"Če ste na optični bralnik postavili dve ločeni sliki ali fotografiji in "
"zagnali predogled &skanlite; samodejno vnaprej izberite različna področja. "
"To vedenje lahko izklopite v pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are satisfied with your choice starting the final batch scan of all "
"selections. The images are saved using the batch renaming feature described "
"in the settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"Če ste zadovoljni s svojo izbiro, začnite končno serijsko skeniranje vseh "
"izbir. Slike se shranijo s funkcijo paketnega preimenovanja, opisano v "
"pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "&skanlite; settings"
msgstr "&skanlite; nastavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By clicking the <guibutton>Settings</guibutton> button, the settings dialog "
"is brought up before the main window. You can choose the most important "
"settings here."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete gumb <guibutton>Nastavitve</guibutton>, se pogovorno okno z "
"nastavitvami prikaže pred glavnim oknom. Tu lahko izberete najpomembnejše "
"nastavitve."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &skanlite; settings dialog"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &skanlite; pogovorno okno z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "&skanlite; settings dialog"
msgstr "&skanlite; pogovorno okno z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preview before saving:"
msgstr "Predogled pred shranjevanjem:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The user can chose to preview the image before saving. In this case the "
"<guilabel>Preview before saving</guilabel> option can be left checked. If "
"the user does not want to preview the image this option should then be "
"unchecked."
msgstr ""
"Uporabnik lahko pred shranjevanjem izbere predogled slike. V tem primeru "
"lahko možnost <guilabel>Predogled pred shranjevanjem</guilabel> pustite "
"označeno. Če si uporabnik ne želi predogleda slike, je treba to možnost "
"počistiti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save Mode:"
msgstr "Način shranjevanja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting allows you to choose how &skanlite; will save the images. If "
"you choose <guilabel>Open the save dialog for every image</guilabel> the "
"save dialog will be opened for every scanned image. If you prefer &skanlite; "
"to auto-save (by auto-generating a name and saving the image in a predefined "
"folder) you can choose <guilabel>Open the save dialog for the first image "
"only</guilabel>. This option will open the following \"Save Location\" "
"dialog for the first scanned image."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev vam omogoča, da izberete, kako &skanlite; bo shranil slike. Če "
"izberete <guilabel>Odpri pogovorno okno za shranjevanje za vsako sliko</"
"guilabel>, se bo pogovorno okno za shranjevanje odprlo za vsako skenirano "
"sliko. Če imate raje &skanlite; za samodejno shranjevanje (s samodejnim "
"ustvarjanjem imena in shranjevanjem slike v vnaprej določeno mapo) lahko "
"izberete <guilabel>Odpri pogovorno okno za shranjevanje samo za prvo sliko</"
"guilabel>. Ta možnost bo odprla naslednje pogovorno okno »Shrani lokacijo« "
"za prvo skenirano sliko."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &skanlite; save location dialog"
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &skanlite; pogovorno okno za shranjevanje lokacije"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "&skanlite; Save Location dialog."
msgstr "&skanlite; Pogovorno okno za shranjevanje lokacije."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save Location:"
msgstr "Shrani lokacijo:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting defines the default save location and file naming. The default "
"save location is your home folder and you can change this location by "
"clicking on the <guibutton>...</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev določa privzeto mesto shranjevanja in poimenovanje datoteke. "
"Privzeta lokacija za shranjevanje je vaša domača mapa in to lokacijo lahko "
"spremenite s klikom na gumb <guibutton>...</guibutton>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name Format:"
msgstr "Oblika imena:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This parameter defines the image prefix for the auto-saved images and is "
"also the suggested name for the image in the save dialog. The auto-saved "
"image will have a numeric suffix (the ### will be replaced by numbers) that "
"is increased every time an image is saved."
msgstr ""
"Ta parameter določa slikovno predpono za samodejno shranjene slike in je "
"tudi predlagano ime za sliko v pogovornem oknu za shranjevanje. Samodejno "
"shranjena slika bo imela številčno pripono (### bo nadomeščena s "
"številkami), ki se poveča vsakič, ko je slika shranjena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can also choose the save format of the file, default is png."
msgstr "Izberete lahko tudi obliko shranjevanja datoteke, privzeto je png."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify save quality:"
msgstr "Določite kakovost shranjevanja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The user can chose to specify the image quality to be used for saving the "
"images. The image quality setting affects the compression level used for "
"saving. If <guilabel>Specify save quality</guilabel> is not checked, the "
"quality is the default value chosen by &Qt;."
msgstr ""
"Uporabnik lahko določi kakovost slike, ki bo uporabljena za shranjevanje "
"slik. Nastavitev kakovosti slike vpliva na stopnjo stiskanja, ki se "
"uporablja za shranjevanje. Če <guilabel>Določi kakovost shranjevanja</"
"guilabel> ni označen, je kakovost privzeta vrednost, ki jo izbere &Qt;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set preview resolution (DPI)"
msgstr "Nastavi ločljivost predogleda (DPI)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&skanlite; is using heuristics to try to get a sane resolution, but if that "
"fails and the resolution is too high or low, then the preview resolution can "
"be manually set with this option."
msgstr ""
"&skanlite; uporablja hevristiko, da poskuša doseči razumno ločljivost, če pa "
"to ne uspe in je ločljivost previsoka ali nizka, lahko ločljivost predogleda "
"ročno nastavite s to možnostjo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disable automatic selections"
msgstr "Onemogoči samodejne izbire"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default automatic selections are enabled; and after a preview, libksane "
"does try to automatically select the images in the preview and should batch "
"scan the selected areas. &eg; if you place two photos on the scanner and do "
"a preview, &skanlite; will automatically add selections of the photos."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto so omogočene samodejne izbire; in po predogledu poskuša libksane "
"samodejno izbrati slike v predogledu in mora paketno skenirati izbrana "
"področja. &eg; če postavite dve fotografiji na skener in naredite predogled, "
"&skanlite; bo samodejno dodal izbor fotografij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If on the other hand you are usually scanning documents it might be that the "
"automatic selection will select a lot of different parts in the documents "
"and you have to manually remove the selections. To avoid that tick the "
"checkbox and disable automatic selection."
msgstr ""
"Če po drugi strani običajno skenirate dokumente, se lahko zgodi, da bo "
"samodejna izbira izbrala veliko različnih delov v dokumentih in boste morali "
"izbire ročno odstraniti. Da bi se temu izognili, označite potrditveno polje "
"in onemogočite samodejno izbiro."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid "Revert scanner options to default values"
msgstr "Povrni možnosti optičnega bralnika na privzete vrednosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The last used settings are reloaded on startup. If you have screwed up the "
"options (for example if you have changed the color correction settings, "
"available in some backends, without knowing what they mean), the image can "
"start to look very odd. For that scenario this option provides a way to "
"revert the setting to the default values, which are a combination of backend "
"and libksane defaults."
msgstr ""
"Zadnje uporabljene nastavitve se znova naložijo ob zagonu. Če ste pokvarili "
"možnosti (na primer, če ste spremenili nastavitve barvne korekcije, ki so na "
"voljo v nekaterih ozadjih, ne da bi vedeli, kaj pomenijo), je lahko slika "
"videti zelo čudna. Za ta scenarij ta možnost ponuja način za povrnitev "
"nastavitve na privzete vrednosti, ki so kombinacija privzetih vrednosti "
"zaledja in libksane."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help, About, Settings and Close"
msgstr "Pomoč, Vizitka, Nastavitve in Zapri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the main window you find the <guibutton>Help</guibutton>, "
"<guibutton>About</guibutton>, <guibutton>Settings</guibutton> and "
"<guibutton>Close</guibutton> buttons."
msgstr ""
"Na dnu glavnega okna najdete gumbe <guibutton>Pomoč</guibutton>, "
"<guibutton>Vizitka</guibutton>, <guibutton>Nastavitve</guibutton> in "
"<guibutton>Zapri</guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Main Window Buttons</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Gumbi glavnega okna</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Main Window Buttons</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Gumbi glavnega okna</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Help</guibutton> button brings up the &kde; Help center with "
"the &skanlite; manual. The <guibutton>About</guibutton> button brings up the "
"&kde; About dialog for &skanlite;. The <guibutton>Settings</guibutton> "
"button displays the settings dialog and the <guibutton>Close</guibutton> "
"button is used to exit &skanlite;."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Pomoč</guibutton> prikliče &kde; Center za pomoč pri "
"&skanlite; priročnik. Gumb <guibutton>Vizitka</guibutton> prikliče &kde; O "
"pogovornem oknu za &skanlite;. Gumb <guibutton>Nastavitve</guibutton> "
"prikaže pogovorno okno z nastavitvami, gumb <guibutton>Zapri</guibutton> pa "
"se uporablja za izhod iz &skanlite;."

